'''Barlen Pyamootoo''' (yavutse 27 Nzeri 1960), ni umwanditsi ukora na filimi wo muri  Mauritius .  Azwiho kuba umuyobozi wa firime ''Bénarès'' . 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 27 Nzeri 1960 i Trou d'Eau Douce, muri Maurice nk'umwana wa gatatu mu muryango wa Tamil ufite barumuna be umunani. Igihe yari afite imyaka 12, nyina yavuye mu rugo ajya gukora mu [[Budage]]. Mu 2006, nyina yishwe na bisi igihe yabaga muri Trou d'Eau Douce. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1977, Pyamootoo yagiye muri kaminuza ya Strasbourg hamwe na se yiga igifaransa n'indimi. Hanyuma yabonye impamyabumenyi ya Diplôme d'études (DEA) mu bumenyi bw'indimi na DEA mu bumenyi bw'uburezi. Nyuma yaje kuba umwarimu w’amabaruwa mu [[Bufaransa]] kuva 1987 kugeza 1993. Mu 1995, yasubiye muri Maurice yitangira kwandika no gutangaza.  Niwe washinze kandi akayobora ibigo bibiri byandika ''Alma'' yashinzwe mu 2005 na ''L'Atelier d'écriture'' yashinzwe mu 2009. 

Amaze kugaruka, yanditse igitabo cye cya mbere ''Bénarès'' . Icyo gihe yari afite imyaka 39. Hanyuma mu 2002, yanditse igitabo cye cya kabiri ''Le Tour de Babilone'' . Muri 2008 yanditse ''Salogi'' icyubahiro nyina. Yatangiye kwandika igitabo gikurikira ''L'île de poissons toxiques'' mu 2002 hanyuma ahagarara muri 2005. Yatangiye imirimo muri 2013 nyuma asohoka muri 2017. 

Mu 2005 yakoze filime ye ya mbere ''Bénarès'' mu rwego rwo guhuza igitabo cye gifite izina rimwe.   Iyi filime ivuga ku basore babiri bazengurutse Maurice aho bahura n'abagore babiri babashimishije.    Hamwe na firime, Pyamootoo abaye umukinnyi wa mbere wa firime wa Maurice wakoresheje igikerewole cya Maurice muri film. 

